<figureCitation captionStart="Figure 1" captionStartId="F1" captionText="Figure 1. A-T Achnanthidium bratanense sp. nov. (LM). A-S size diminution series showing variation in valve outline A holotype specimen A-D, F-I, K, M, N, R raphe valves E, J, L, O-Q, S rapheless valves T frustule in girdle view. Scale bar: 10 μm." figureDoi="10.3897/phytokeys.188.77882.figure1" httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/635397" pageId="0" pageNumber="167">1A</figureCitation>
